msgid "The API is provided for legitimate task-management automation. You may not place an unreasonable load on the service — for example by polling at excessive rates, ignoring rate-limit responses, or scripting bulk operations designed to degrade the service for others. We may throttle or suspend access that interferes with the stability of the platform."
